{"title":"矿工的眼睛","authors":["雁翼"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天轮颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山峰连着山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天轮排着天轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么像矿工的身影——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云霞上的一排巨人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把手伸进山的深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掏出地下的乌金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿去吧，我的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这光、这热、这力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有你儿子的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这颗赤心……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车飞出矿井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车驰进矿山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我脚下的两股铁道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非是连环的轮盘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绞着一串串斗车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日夜夜旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绞出地下的煤海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去灌溉祖国的工业之田……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿区之夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯的楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯的湖滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯的花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯的马路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸进大地的深渊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地下汇成灯的大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进每一个掌子面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着风镐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着电钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着煤的长流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔回灯的地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这灯的世界里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都有灯盏作伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工顶着灯采煤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊事员顶着灯送饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司机顶着灯开车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医生顶着灯诊断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年老的矿长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也顶着灯指挥生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是矿工的梦里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是灯光闪闪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再硬的岩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再厚的煤层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡不断矿工的视线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮不住矿工的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那心灵优美的光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在两眼里集中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿透千丈大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注视地面上的活动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的每一件胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在目光里得到反映，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那急转的风镐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是证明……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}